{
  "video_id": "bPfn01Ndc1g",
  "title": "Arthur Ganson: Moving sculpture",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 18330.0,
      "end_time": 20330.0,
      "text": "A few words about how I got started,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 20330.0,
      "end_time": 24330.0,
      "text": "and it has a lot to do with happiness, actually."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 24330.0,
      "end_time": 27330.0,
      "text": "When I was a very young child, I was extremely introverted"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 27330.0,
      "end_time": 30330.0,
      "text": "and very much to myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30330.0,
      "end_time": 33330.0,
      "text": "And, kind of as a way of surviving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 33330.0,
      "end_time": 36330.0,
      "text": "I would go into my own very personal space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 36330.0,
      "end_time": 38330.0,
      "text": "and I would make things."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38330.0,
      "end_time": 40330.0,
      "text": "I would make things for people"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40330.0,
      "end_time": 44330.0,
      "text": "as a way of, you know, giving, showing them my love."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44330.0,
      "end_time": 47330.0,
      "text": "I would go into these private places,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47330.0,
      "end_time": 51330.0,
      "text": "and I would put my ideas and my passions into objects --"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51330.0,
      "end_time": 54330.0,
      "text": "and sort of learning how to speak with my hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54330.0,
      "end_time": 58330.0,
      "text": "So, the whole activity of working with my hands and creating objects"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 58330.0,
      "end_time": 63330.0,
      "text": "is very much connected with not only the idea realm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 63330.0,
      "end_time": 66330.0,
      "text": "but also with very much the feeling realm."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 67330.0,
      "end_time": 71330.0,
      "text": "And the ideas are very disparate."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 71330.0,
      "end_time": 74330.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to show you many different kinds of pieces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 74330.0,
      "end_time": 77330.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s no real connection between one or the other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 77330.0,
      "end_time": 79330.0,
      "text": "except that they sort of come out of my brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 79330.0,
      "end_time": 83330.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re all different sort of thoughts that are triggered"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 83330.0,
      "end_time": 87330.0,
      "text": "by looking at life, and seeing nature and seeing objects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 87330.0,
      "end_time": 91330.0,
      "text": "and just having kind of playful random thoughts about things."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 91330.0,
      "end_time": 99330.0,
      "text": "When I was a child, I started to explore motion."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 99330.0,
      "end_time": 101330.0,
      "text": "I fell in love with the way things moved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 101330.0,
      "end_time": 106330.0,
      "text": "so I started to explore motion by making little flipbooks."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 106330.0,
      "end_time": 110330.0,
      "text": "And this is one that I did, probably like when I was around seventh grade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 110330.0,
      "end_time": 113330.0,
      "text": "and I remember when I was doing this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 113330.0,
      "end_time": 116330.0,
      "text": "I was thinking about that little rock there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 116330.0,
      "end_time": 121330.0,
      "text": "and the pathway of the vehicles as they would fly through the air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 121330.0,
      "end_time": 123330.0,
      "text": "and how the characters --"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 123330.0,
      "end_time": 124330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) --"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 124330.0,
      "end_time": 126330.0,
      "text": "would come shooting out of the car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 126330.0,
      "end_time": 133329.0,
      "text": "so, on my mind, I was thinking about the trajectory of the vehicles."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 133330.0,
      "end_time": 136330.0,
      "text": "And of course, when you&#39;re a little kid, there&#39;s always destruction."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 136330.0,
      "end_time": 138330.0,
      "text": "So, it has to end with this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 138330.0,
      "end_time": 139330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) --"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 139330.0,
      "end_time": 141330.0,
      "text": "gratuitous violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 141330.0,
      "end_time": 143330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 143330.0,
      "end_time": 149330.0,
      "text": "So that was how I first started to explore the way things moved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 149330.0,
      "end_time": 151330.0,
      "text": "and expressed it."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 151330.0,
      "end_time": 153330.0,
      "text": "Now, when I went to college,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 153330.0,
      "end_time": 160330.0,
      "text": "I found myself making fairly complicated, fragile machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 160330.0,
      "end_time": 163330.0,
      "text": "And this really came about"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 163330.0,
      "end_time": 166330.0,
      "text": "from having many different kinds of interests."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 166330.0,
      "end_time": 169330.0,
      "text": "When I was in high school, I loved to program computers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 169330.0,
      "end_time": 173330.0,
      "text": "so I sort of liked the logical flow of events."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 174330.0,
      "end_time": 179330.0,
      "text": "I was also very interested in perhaps going into surgery"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 179330.0,
      "end_time": 181330.0,
      "text": "and becoming a surgeon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 181330.0,
      "end_time": 183330.0,
      "text": "because it meant working with my hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 183330.0,
      "end_time": 186330.0,
      "text": "in a very focused, intense way."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 186330.0,
      "end_time": 188330.0,
      "text": "So, I started taking art courses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 188330.0,
      "end_time": 191330.0,
      "text": "and I found a way to make sculpture"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 191330.0,
      "end_time": 195330.0,
      "text": "that brought together my love for being very precise with my hands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 195330.0,
      "end_time": 205330.0,
      "text": "with coming up with different kinds of logical flows of energy through a system."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 205330.0,
      "end_time": 211330.0,
      "text": "And also, working with wire -- everything that I did"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 211330.0,
      "end_time": 217330.0,
      "text": "was both a visual and a mechanical engineering decision"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 217330.0,
      "end_time": 219330.0,
      "text": "at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 219330.0,
      "end_time": 221330.0,
      "text": "So, I was able to sort of exercise all of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 221330.0,
      "end_time": 227330.0,
      "text": "Now, this kind of machine is as close as I can get to painting."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 227330.0,
      "end_time": 232330.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s full of many little trivial end points,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 232330.0,
      "end_time": 237330.0,
      "text": "like there&#39;s a little foot here that just drags around in circles"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 237330.0,
      "end_time": 239330.0,
      "text": "and it doesn&#39;t really mean anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 239330.0,
      "end_time": 244330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really just for the sort of joy of its own triviality."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 245330.0,
      "end_time": 248330.0,
      "text": "The connection I have with engineering"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 248330.0,
      "end_time": 253330.0,
      "text": "is the same as any other engineer, in that I love to solve problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 253330.0,
      "end_time": 255330.0,
      "text": "I love to figure things out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 255330.0,
      "end_time": 260330.0,
      "text": "but the end result of what I&#39;m doing is really completely ambiguous."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 261329.0,
      "end_time": 263330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 263330.0,
      "end_time": 265330.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s pretty ambiguous."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 265330.0,
      "end_time": 266330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 267330.0,
      "end_time": 272330.0,
      "text": "The next piece that is going to come up"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 272330.0,
      "end_time": 281330.0,
      "text": "is an example of a kind of machine that is fairly complex."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 282330.0,
      "end_time": 284330.0,
      "text": "I gave myself the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 284330.0,
      "end_time": 286330.0,
      "text": "Since I&#39;m always liking to solve problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 286330.0,
      "end_time": 290330.0,
      "text": "I gave myself the problem of turning a crank in one direction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 290330.0,
      "end_time": 293330.0,
      "text": "and solving all of the mechanical problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 293330.0,
      "end_time": 296330.0,
      "text": "for getting this little man to walk back and forth."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 297330.0,
      "end_time": 301330.0,
      "text": "So, when I started this, I didn&#39;t have an overall plan for the machine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 302330.0,
      "end_time": 305330.0,
      "text": "but I did have a sense of the gesture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 305330.0,
      "end_time": 309330.0,
      "text": "and a sense of the shape and how it would occupy space."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 309330.0,
      "end_time": 312330.0,
      "text": "And then it was a matter of starting from one point"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 312330.0,
      "end_time": 315330.0,
      "text": "and sort of building to that final point."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 316330.0,
      "end_time": 320330.0,
      "text": "That little gear there switches back and forth to change direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 321330.0,
      "end_time": 323330.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s a little found object."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 325330.0,
      "end_time": 328330.0,
      "text": "So a lot of the pieces that I&#39;ve made,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 328330.0,
      "end_time": 331330.0,
      "text": "they involve found objects."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 332330.0,
      "end_time": 340330.0,
      "text": "And it really -- it&#39;s almost like doing visual puns all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 340330.0,
      "end_time": 343330.0,
      "text": "When I see objects, I imagine them in motion."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 343330.0,
      "end_time": 345330.0,
      "text": "I imagine what can be said with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 345330.0,
      "end_time": 349330.0,
      "text": "This next one here, \"Machine with Wishbone,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 349330.0,
      "end_time": 356330.0,
      "text": "it came about from playing with this wishbone after dinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 356330.0,
      "end_time": 358330.0,
      "text": "You know, they say, never play with your food --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 358330.0,
      "end_time": 360330.0,
      "text": "but I always play with things."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 360330.0,
      "end_time": 362330.0,
      "text": "So, I had this wishbone, and I thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 362330.0,
      "end_time": 365330.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s kind of like a cowboy who&#39;s been on his horse for too long."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 365330.0,
      "end_time": 366330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 366330.0,
      "end_time": 369330.0,
      "text": "And I started to make him walk across the table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 369330.0,
      "end_time": 372330.0,
      "text": "and I thought, \"Oh, I can make a little machine that will do that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 374330.0,
      "end_time": 380330.0,
      "text": "So, I made this device, linked it up, and the wishbone walks."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 380330.0,
      "end_time": 383330.0,
      "text": "And because the wishbone is bone -- it&#39;s animal --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 383330.0,
      "end_time": 388330.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s sort of a point where I think we can enter into it."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 389330.0,
      "end_time": 391330.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s the whole piece."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 391330.0,
      "end_time": 392330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 392330.0,
      "end_time": 395330.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s about that big."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 395330.0,
      "end_time": 399330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 400330.0,
      "end_time": 405330.0,
      "text": "This kind of work is also very much like puppetry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 405330.0,
      "end_time": 409330.0,
      "text": "where the found object is, in a sense, the puppet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 409330.0,
      "end_time": 414330.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m the puppeteer at first, because I&#39;m playing with an object."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 414330.0,
      "end_time": 418330.0,
      "text": "But then I make the machine, which is sort of the stand-in for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 418330.0,
      "end_time": 421330.0,
      "text": "and it is able to achieve the action that I want."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 423330.0,
      "end_time": 430330.0,
      "text": "The next piece I&#39;ll show you is a much more conceptual thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 430330.0,
      "end_time": 433330.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a little piece called \"Cory&#39;s Yellow Chair.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 434330.0,
      "end_time": 439330.0,
      "text": "I had this image in my mind, when I saw my son&#39;s little chair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 439330.0,
      "end_time": 443330.0,
      "text": "and I saw it explode up and out."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 444330.0,
      "end_time": 446330.0,
      "text": "And --"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 448330.0,
      "end_time": 451330.0,
      "text": "so the way I saw this in my mind at first,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 451330.0,
      "end_time": 455330.0,
      "text": "was that the pieces would explode up and out with infinite speed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 455330.0,
      "end_time": 457330.0,
      "text": "and the pieces would move far out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 457330.0,
      "end_time": 459330.0,
      "text": "and then they would begin to be pulled back"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 459330.0,
      "end_time": 461330.0,
      "text": "with a kind of a gravitational feel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 461330.0,
      "end_time": 465330.0,
      "text": "to the point where they would approach infinite speed back to the center."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 465330.0,
      "end_time": 468330.0,
      "text": "And they would coalesce for just a moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 468330.0,
      "end_time": 471330.0,
      "text": "so you could perceive that there was a chair there."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 471330.0,
      "end_time": 477330.0,
      "text": "For me, it&#39;s kind of a feeling about the fleetingness of the present moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 477330.0,
      "end_time": 479330.0,
      "text": "and I wanted to express that."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 479330.0,
      "end_time": 484330.0,
      "text": "Now, the machine is -- in this case, it&#39;s a real approximation of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 484330.0,
      "end_time": 487330.0,
      "text": "because obviously you can&#39;t move physical matter"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 487330.0,
      "end_time": 491330.0,
      "text": "infinitely with infinite speed and have it stop instantaneously."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 491330.0,
      "end_time": 495330.0,
      "text": "This whole thing is about four feet wide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 495330.0,
      "end_time": 498330.0,
      "text": "and the chair itself is only about a few inches."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 498330.0,
      "end_time": 503330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 503330.0,
      "end_time": 506330.0,
      "text": "Now, this is a funny sort of conceptual thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 506330.0,
      "end_time": 511330.0,
      "text": "and yesterday we were talking about Danny Hillis&#39; \"10,000 Year Clock.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 511330.0,
      "end_time": 513329.0,
      "text": "So, we have a motor here on the left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 513330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516330.00000000006,
      "text": "and it goes through a gear train."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 516330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521330.00000000006,
      "text": "There are 12 pairs of 50:1 reductions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 521330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526330.0,
      "text": "so that means that the final speed of that gear on the end"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 526330.0,
      "end_time": 530330.0,
      "text": "is so slow that it would take two trillion years to turn once."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 530330.0,
      "end_time": 533330.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve invented it in concrete, because it doesn&#39;t really matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 533330.0,
      "end_time": 534330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 534330.0,
      "end_time": 536330.0,
      "text": "Because it could run all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 536330.0,
      "end_time": 537330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 537330.0,
      "end_time": 541330.0,
      "text": "Now, a completely different thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 541330.0,
      "end_time": 545330.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m always imagining myself in different situations."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 545330.0,
      "end_time": 547330.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m imagining myself as a machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 547330.0,
      "end_time": 549330.0,
      "text": "What would I love?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 549330.0,
      "end_time": 551330.0,
      "text": "I would love to be bathed in oil."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 551330.0,
      "end_time": 552330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 552330.0,
      "end_time": 557330.0,
      "text": "So, this machine does nothing but just bathe itself in oil."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 557330.0,
      "end_time": 559330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 559330.0,
      "end_time": 563330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 563330.0,
      "end_time": 566330.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s really, just sort of --"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 566330.0,
      "end_time": 569330.0,
      "text": "for me, it was just really about the lusciousness of oil."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 569330.0,
      "end_time": 570330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 570330.0,
      "end_time": 573330.0,
      "text": "And then, I got a call from a friend"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 573330.0,
      "end_time": 576330.0,
      "text": "who wanted to have a show of erotic art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 576330.0,
      "end_time": 578330.0,
      "text": "and I didn&#39;t have any pieces."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 578330.0,
      "end_time": 582330.0,
      "text": "But when she suggested to be in the show, this piece came to mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 582330.0,
      "end_time": 586330.0,
      "text": "So, it&#39;s sort of related, but you can see it&#39;s much more overtly erotic."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 588330.0,
      "end_time": 591330.0,
      "text": "And this one I call \"Machine with Grease.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 591330.0,
      "end_time": 593330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just continually ejaculating, and it&#39;s --"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 593330.0,
      "end_time": 594330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) --"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 594330.0,
      "end_time": 597330.0,
      "text": "this is a happy machine, I&#39;ll tell you."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 597330.0,
      "end_time": 598330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 598330.0,
      "end_time": 600330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s definitely happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 602330.0,
      "end_time": 605330.0,
      "text": "From an engineering point of view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 605330.0,
      "end_time": 607330.0,
      "text": "this is just a little four-bar linkage."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 607330.0,
      "end_time": 612330.0,
      "text": "And then again, this is a found object, a little fan that I found."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 612330.0,
      "end_time": 615330.0,
      "text": "And I thought, what about the gesture of opening the fan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 615330.0,
      "end_time": 618330.0,
      "text": "and how simply could I state something."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 618330.0,
      "end_time": 626330.0,
      "text": "And, in a case like this, I&#39;m trying to make something which is clear"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 626330.0,
      "end_time": 631330.0,
      "text": "but also not suggestive of any particular kind of animal or plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 633330.0,
      "end_time": 638330.0,
      "text": "For me, the process is very important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 638330.0,
      "end_time": 640330.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;m inventing machines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 640330.0,
      "end_time": 643330.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m also inventing tools to make machines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 643330.0,
      "end_time": 646330.0,
      "text": "and the whole thing is all sort of wrapped up from the beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 646330.0,
      "end_time": 649330.0,
      "text": "So this is a little wire-bending tool."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 649330.0,
      "end_time": 652330.0,
      "text": "After many years of bending gears with a pair of pliers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 652330.0,
      "end_time": 655330.0,
      "text": "I made that tool, and then I made this other tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 655330.0,
      "end_time": 658330.0,
      "text": "for sort of centering gears very quickly --"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 659330.0,
      "end_time": 662330.0,
      "text": "sort of developing my own little world of technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 662330.0,
      "end_time": 668330.0,
      "text": "My life completely changed when I found a spot welder."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 668330.0,
      "end_time": 669330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 669330.0,
      "end_time": 671330.0,
      "text": "And that was that tool."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 671330.0,
      "end_time": 673330.0,
      "text": "It completely changed what I could do."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 673330.0,
      "end_time": 677330.0,
      "text": "Now here, I&#39;m going to do a very poor job of silver soldering."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 678330.0,
      "end_time": 683330.0,
      "text": "This is not the way they teach you to silver solder when you&#39;re in school."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 683330.0,
      "end_time": 685330.0,
      "text": "I just like, throw it in."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 685330.0,
      "end_time": 687330.0,
      "text": "I mean, real jewelers put little bits of solder in."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 688330.0,
      "end_time": 691330.0,
      "text": "So, that&#39;s a finished gear."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 692330.0,
      "end_time": 694330.0,
      "text": "When I moved to Boston,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 694330.0,
      "end_time": 699330.0,
      "text": "I joined a group called the World Sculpture Racing Society."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 699330.0,
      "end_time": 700330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 700330.0,
      "end_time": 707330.0,
      "text": "And the idea, their premise was that we wanted to show"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 707330.0,
      "end_time": 709330.0,
      "text": "pieces of sculpture on the street,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 709330.0,
      "end_time": 713330.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;d be no subjective decision about what was the best."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 713330.0,
      "end_time": 715330.0,
      "text": "It would be -- whatever came across the finish line first would be the winner."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 715330.0,
      "end_time": 716330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 716330.0,
      "end_time": 720330.0,
      "text": "So I made -- this is my first racing sculpture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 720330.0,
      "end_time": 722330.0,
      "text": "and I thought, \"Oh, I&#39;m going to make a cart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 722330.0,
      "end_time": 724330.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to have it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 724330.0,
      "end_time": 726330.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to have my hand writing &#39;faster,&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 726330.0,
      "end_time": 730330.0,
      "text": "so as I run down the street, the cart&#39;s going to talk to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 730330.0,
      "end_time": 733330.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s going to go, &#39;Faster, faster!&#39; \""
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 733330.0,
      "end_time": 735330.0,
      "text": "So, that&#39;s what it does."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 735330.0,
      "end_time": 736330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 736330.0,
      "end_time": 741330.0,
      "text": "But then in the end, what I decided"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 741330.0,
      "end_time": 744330.0,
      "text": "was every time you finish writing the word,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 744330.0,
      "end_time": 748330.0,
      "text": "I would stop and I would give the card to somebody on the side of the road."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 748330.0,
      "end_time": 751330.0,
      "text": "So I would never win the race because I&#39;m always stopping."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 751330.0,
      "end_time": 753330.0,
      "text": "But I had a lot of fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 753330.0,
      "end_time": 759330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 759330.0,
      "end_time": 763330.0,
      "text": "Now, I only have two and a half minutes -- I&#39;m going to play this."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 763330.0,
      "end_time": 769330.0,
      "text": "This is a piece that, for me, is in some ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 769330.0,
      "end_time": 771330.0,
      "text": "the most complete kind of piece."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 771330.0,
      "end_time": 773330.0,
      "text": "Because when I was a kid, I also played a lot of guitar."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 773330.0,
      "end_time": 777330.0,
      "text": "And when I had this thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 777330.0,
      "end_time": 779330.0,
      "text": "I was imagining that I would make --"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 779330.0,
      "end_time": 782330.0,
      "text": "I would have a whole machine theater evening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 782330.0,
      "end_time": 784330.0,
      "text": "where I would -- you would have an audience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 784330.0,
      "end_time": 788330.0,
      "text": "the curtain would open, and you&#39;d be entertained by machines on stage."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 788330.0,
      "end_time": 791330.0,
      "text": "So, I imagined a very simple gestural dance"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 791330.0,
      "end_time": 799330.0,
      "text": "that would be between a machine and just a very simple chair, and ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 807330.0,
      "end_time": 811330.0,
      "text": "When I&#39;m making these pieces, I&#39;m always trying to find a point"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 811330.0,
      "end_time": 822330.0,
      "text": "where I&#39;m saying something very clearly and it&#39;s very simple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 822330.0,
      "end_time": 825330.0,
      "text": "but also at the same time it&#39;s very ambiguous."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 825330.0,
      "end_time": 830330.0,
      "text": "And I think there&#39;s a point between simplicity and ambiguity"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 830330.0,
      "end_time": 836330.0,
      "text": "which can allow a viewer to perhaps take something from it."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 839330.0,
      "end_time": 843330.0,
      "text": "And that leads me to the thought that all of these pieces"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 843330.0,
      "end_time": 847330.0,
      "text": "start off in my own mind, in my heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 847330.0,
      "end_time": 854330.0,
      "text": "and I do my best at finding ways to express them with materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 854330.0,
      "end_time": 856330.0,
      "text": "and it always feels really crude."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 856330.0,
      "end_time": 858330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s always a struggle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 859330.0,
      "end_time": 863330.0,
      "text": "but somehow I manage to sort of get this thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 863330.0,
      "end_time": 867330.0,
      "text": "out into an object, and then it&#39;s there, OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 867330.0,
      "end_time": 869330.0,
      "text": "It means nothing at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 869330.0,
      "end_time": 871330.0,
      "text": "The object itself just means nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 871330.0,
      "end_time": 876330.0,
      "text": "Once it&#39;s perceived, and someone brings it into their own mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 876330.0,
      "end_time": 881330.0,
      "text": "then there&#39;s a cycle that has been completed."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 881330.0,
      "end_time": 883330.0,
      "text": "And to me, that&#39;s the most important thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 883330.0,
      "end_time": 888330.0,
      "text": "because, ever since being a kid, I&#39;ve wanted to communicate my passion and love."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 888330.0,
      "end_time": 893330.0,
      "text": "And that means the complete cycle of coming from inside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 893330.0,
      "end_time": 898330.0,
      "text": "out to the physical, to someone perceiving it."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 901330.0,
      "end_time": 905330.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ll just let this chair come down."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 933330.0,
      "end_time": 934330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 934330.0,
      "end_time": 935330.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 935330.0,
      "end_time": 938330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}